Description

New Punjab Government Jobs have been published by Punjab State Transmission Corporation for the vacancies of Asst. Lineman, JE, LDC, and others. If you are finding a government job in Punjab then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Punjab, from the 26-04-2021, and till the 17-05-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Punjab and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

Mode of application is Online

  • The application fee for SC candidates is only Rs. 566/-
  • The application fee for PWD candidates is only Rs. 708/-
  • The application fee for EWS candidates is only Rs. 566/-
  • The application fee for the rest of the candidates is only Rs. 1416/-

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 26-04-2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is17-05-2021 (Upto 05:00 PM)
  • Last Date for Depositing Fee at State Bank of India: 19-05-2021 (Up to Closing of Bank Business Hours)

Educational qualification to apply for PSTCL Asst. Lineman, JE, LDC, and others vacancies in Punjab:

  • To apply for Asst. Lineman, JE, LDC, and other posts in Punjab, your BE/BTECH/Diploma/B.Com must be completed from a recognized University

Age Limit Criteria

  • For AE (OT)/ Electrical, Civil, Account Officer, Asst Manager/ HR, IT Candidate, you should be between 20 to 37  years old.
  • For Divisional Accountant, JE/ Sub Station, Civil, Communication, Telephone Mechanic, LDC/ Typist, Accounts Candidate, you should be between 20 to 37  years old. 

PSTCLAsst. Lineman, JE, LDC, and others Pay Scale:

According to the information given by the Punjab Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is fiven below.

  • Clerk - Rs.6400-20200+3400
  • Revenue Accountant - Rs.10900-34800+5400
  • Junior Engineer/Electrical - Rs.10900-34800+5350
  • Assistant Lineman - 6400-20200 (+ 3400 Grade Pay).
  • Assistant Sub Station attendant —

How to apply for PSTCL Asst. Lineman, JE, LDC Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Punjab. Fill in your details and submit it

Or follow all the steps given below,

  •  First, go to the official website of PSTCL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY PSTCL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
